Task 7: Open the Frontend in a Browser
	
	-Expose the frontend service using Minikube.
	-Command used to access the service
		$ kubectl port-forward service/frontend 8080:80

	-Browser output showing the running app
    C:\Users\repo\DevOps\devops-course\k8s>minikube service frontend
    ┌───────────┬──────────┬─────────────┬───────────────────────────┐
    │ NAMESPACE │   NAME   │ TARGET PORT │            URL            │
